DESCRIPTION:New at the J! Mahjong Masters is a once-a-month free play socia
	l event for advanced and expert mahjong players. Bring friends\, meet new 
	ones\, and grab a nosh at these exclusive sessions open only to the season
	ed players in our community.   We recommend that all participants be comfo
	rtable playing at a quick pace and have a complete understanding of the ru
	les and game.   These sessions are free but we ask you to register in adva
	nce\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/mahjong-masters-free-
